## ğŸ”„ CI/CD Workflows

### Development (`dev` branch)

- Code quality checks (formatting, linting)
- Basic RAG validation
- Docker build with `dev-{sha}` tags

### UAT (`uat` branch)

- Strict quality gates
- Full RAG system testing
- Docker build with `uat-{sha}` tags

### Production (releases)

- Comprehensive testing + security scans
- Container health checks
- Production-ready deployment

## ğŸš¢ Quick Start

### Local Development

```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run FastAPI server
python main.py

# Test RAG system
python Ai_search/test_rag.py

# Test Avatar Generator
python Avatar_generator/test_avatar.py
```

### Docker

```bash
# Build image
docker build -t ibc-365-be .

# Run container
docker run -p 8000:8000 ibc-365-be
```

